text: Goudavelly also Goudelli is a village and panchayat in Rangareddy district, AP, India. It comes under Medchal mandal. It is 15 kilometers away from Secuderabad. The Outer Ring Road, Hyderabad has a major junction in this village. Category:Villages in Ranga Reddy district
title: Goudavelly, Ranga Reddy district
